{"tid":1760761,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新田購物城月蝕百萬如「死城」8月結業 黃定光嘆時不予我：好心傷","createTime":"2019-11-28T12:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T13:03:38.000Z","uid":1221,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6102e952ce58feae351601fed49144549d1a104d","tid":1760761,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191128/_2019112812472673603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191128%2F_2019112812472673603.jpg&h=5c07e735&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新田購物城開業至今一直人迹罕至，被形容為「死城」，有遺原先分流水貨客及內地客的目的，購物城已靜悄悄地於今年8月結業。項目牽頭人立法會議員黃定光感慨結業，無奈說「好心傷，好多嘢已經事與願違、時不予我」。他說，項目營運籌備了2年半，期間因個人遊政策改變，加上修例風波未息，訪港旅客量大減，「無客到」難支撐，最終「好難搞落去」，要結業。<br />\n<br />\n黃定光接受傳媒訪問時承認結業一事，他說，「我哋每個月要交好多唔同費用，但因冇任何收入，而我哋每月有關水、電、保安、管場地開支超過100萬元，喺咁情況下，我哋冇辦法再堅持落去。 」<br />\n<br />\n他又指，未計已投入的1.8億港元建設費，更要月蝕百萬港元，至今未收過一元租金，經各人商議後只能離場止蝕。他透露，已將土地交還發展商。<br />\n<br />\n黃定光說，早前計劃興建購物城，有超過200幾家店舖響應，到正式簽署時只有27間，正式開業時只有17間，以致場面冷清。他又指，經營者擔心經營的持續性，對於有指場內仍有店舖正在營業時，他說未知實際情況，回到場內再作了解。又補充，「其實佢哋都已經難以經營，可以話到雞毛鴨血，我哋又已經幫唔到乜，唔可以話佢哋，所以我去了解下先。」<br />\n<br />\n對於購城物結業，他無奈地說，「係好心傷&hellip;時不予我，依家仲要發生咁多事，係好難搞落去。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/9f/11lp2p2n.jpg/revision/latest/top-crop/width/220/height/220?cb=20120511155252\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F9f%2F11lp2p2n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Ftop-crop%2Fwidth%2F220%2Fheight%2F220%3Fcb%3D20120511155252&h=3ee8729b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃定光對結業表示無奈，說「時不予我」"},{"pid":"21ea4123bdd79c3c98329b49d9ffbbe14cb6ff2a","tid":1760761,"uid":298354,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:36:53.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"f524cd6f04462aa121a0cddabc6ed99869077bb7","tid":1760761,"uid":40625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"a08f02536501ad7b8a63e7ea04d5cc2cbf067f56","tid":1760761,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:55:45.000Z","msg":"同前海基地、雄安新區一尻樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb74c01fbaa601ab46498e6e06a5201aa819afe3","tid":1760761,"uid":80243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"修唔修例都無人去架啦"},{"pid":"84a23e9f9a80defde34e63a33ae454e30ae072d4","tid":1760761,"uid":334806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"關咩事<br />\n無示威之前已經死城咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8281a378b07ad27f89af1388bc5e5eba515aad","tid":1760761,"uid":286131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84a23e9f9a80defde34e63a33ae454e30ae072d4","tid":1760761,"uid":334806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:02:02.000Z","msg":"關咩事<br />\n無示威之前已經死城咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一開始已經當人水魚"},{"pid":"e3fc37b0a013f04f38ba8456df0fff454e538d00","tid":1760761,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T13:03:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ppoWNfind_o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FppoWNfind_o&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtA2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=efbd14fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ppoWNfind_o</a> <br />\n上年9月嘅片<br />\n咪又係死城咁"}]}